我们这几周都过得不容易
Look, we have both had a rough go over these past couple of weeks.

47
00:02:33,620 --> 00:02:35,060
而且
And, uh...

48
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:38,330
我知道你的牺牲很大
I know what you gave up wasn't easy.

49
00:02:38,330 --> 00:02:41,900
