Maybe we ought to take the night off --

50
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:45,100
去看部电影  找一两个酒吧喝酒
Go see a flick, hit a bar or two,

51
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:47,170
好好玩玩
have some fun.

52
00:02:47,170 --> 00:02:49,840
你还记得那滋味吧  小萨姆
You remember fun, don't you, Sammy?

53
00:02:57,180 --> 00:02:58,580
